Package: EchoPickList
Title: A package to design microplate experiments and to generate picklist for use with the Echo acoustic dispenser
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Erick", "Arroyo-Perez", , "erickarroyo1312@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Contains functions to design microplate experiments with combinatorial conditions that can be added as a solution with the Echo acoustic dispenser, as well as functions to generate picklist ready to use with the Beckman Echo software.
